      "text": "Hundreds of millions of people today can hear on the radio important statements by public men, statements which in earlier times could have been heard by few. It is a question whether at any time in history a man has been able to make his voice heard by as many as a hundred thousand people at the same time. Without the telephone and the radio a man can be heard only as far as his voice can carry.",
